NAME
	lockout

ACCESS LEVEL
	archwizard

SYNOPSIS
	lockout list
	lockout add <ip-number>
	lockout remove <entry>

DESCRIPTION
	Disallow the creation of new characters from a site. Existing
	characters can still log in from the site. People who try to
	create a new character, can still do so by using the new name
	"application". Then the administration can judge the application
	of the new player.

OPTIONS
	list	- list the currently sites locked out;
	add	- add site <ip-number> to the list of sites locked out;
	remove	- remove the lockout-status of a site where <entry> is
		  the index of the site in the "lockout list"
		  enumeration.

SEE ALSO
	block
